### ===== PROPOSAL ENDPOINTS =====


### Get All Proposals
GET http://localhost:3001/api/proposals


### Get Proposal by ID (id=2)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/proposals/2

### Create Proposal (userId=2, member sameer)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/proposals
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 2,
    "description": "Upgrade office equipment and computers",
    "cost": 5000
}

### Create Another Proposal (userId=3, member rafay)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/proposals
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 3,
    "description": "Team building and training program",
    "cost": 3000
}

### Update Proposal (id=1)
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/proposals/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "description": "Upgrade office equipment with latest technology and software",
    "cost": 6000
}

### Delete Proposal (id=1)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/proposals/2

### Get Proposals by User (userId=2)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/proposals/user/2


### Create Proposal by userId=2
POST http://localhost:3001/api/proposals
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 2,
    "description": "Proposal from sameer",
    "cost": 3000
}

### Create Proposal by userId=3
POST http://localhost:3001/api/proposals
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 3,
    "description": "Proposal from rafay",
    "cost": 4000
}

### Get Proposals for Voting (userId=2, excludes their own)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/proposals/voting/2



### ===== VOTING ENDPOINTS =====

### Cast Vote (userId=2 votes on proposalId=2 with score=3)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/votes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 2,
    "proposalId": 2,
    "score": 3
}


### Cast Vote with Invalid User (userId=999)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/votes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 1,
    "proposalId": 3,
    "score": 2
}


### Update Vote (userId=2, proposalId=2, change score to 1)
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/votes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 1,
    "proposalId": 3,
    "score": 1
}


### Delete Vote (userId=2, proposalId=1)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/votes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 2,
    "proposalId": 2
}

### Try to Delete Already Deleted Vote (should return error)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/votes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 1,
    "proposalId": 3
}


### Get Proposals User Has Voted On (userId=2)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/votes/user/1



### ===== SUMMARY ENDPOINTS =====

### Set Budget (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/budget
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 10000
}

### Get Current Budget
GET http://localhost:3001/api/budget

### Get Summary with Budget and Accepted Proposals
GET http://localhost:3001/api/summary


### ===== PHASE MANAGEMENT ENDPOINTS =====

### Get Current Phase
GET http://localhost:3001/api/phase/current

### Transition to Phase 1 (PROPOSAL)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/phase/transition
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phase": 1
}

### Transition to Phase 2 (VOTING)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/phase/transition
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phase": 2
}

### Transition to Phase 3 (SUMMARY)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/phase/transition
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phase": 3
}

### Get Current Phase (should be 3)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/phase/current

### Try Invalid Phase (should return error)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/phase/transition
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phase": 5
}

#-----------------------------

### Restart System (Clear all proposals and votes, back to Phase 0)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/phase/restart
Content-Type: application/json

{}